column5: Received an email yesterday from Nakina and was told there is snow on the ground. None in Ohio yet. They can keep the snow.
We had snow saturday morning in Winnipeg.
Email from nakina saying 8" of snow on ground.
Snow at my house. Some friends rode their snowmobiles to the Trestle Inn in Finland MN and are having lunch right now.
Lots of snow in the vermilion bay area.hwys were closed yesterday.had to recut trails into my deer stands as snow was so heavy everything was bent over and a ton of downed trees.real mess.

October 5, 2012, I was on Little Vermilion Lake when we had about 15" of snow. Pilots did a lot of sharing of fuel and east to west flying to help each other get early, up north, moose hunters back to Red Lake.
